    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header display-4 text-center">
        About Wecasual
      </div>
      <div class="card-body about-text">
        <h3 class="card-title">The spirit of real life recreational sports leagues brought to eSports</h3>
        <ul class="card-text">
          <li>Wecasual is a Dota 2 community that <b>hosts games all week every week</b> for players looking to have a fun and positive Dota 2 experience.</li>
          <li>Wecasual is building a recreational sports league feel in eSports. Wecasual is the place to come hangout and have fun a couple of nights a week.</li>
          <li>Wecasual is a <b>toxic-player free environment</b> where players are guaranteed nice teammates!</li>

        </ul>

        <h3 class="card-title">It's more than just Dota 2</h3>
        <ul class="card-text">
          <li>At Wecasual it is not just about playing Dota 2. Wecasual is the place to <b>unwind and chill out</b> for people who love Dota 2.</li>
          <li>Before and after every game we offer activities to encourage players to <b>hangout in our Discord</b> with other members</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="card-title">How does Wecasual work?</h3>
        <ul class="card-text">
          <li>When you sign up for Wecasual you will get a link to join our Discord community.</li>
          <li>You will then be able to see upcoming games that you can sign up for!</li>
          <li>You can play in as many games as you want per week.</li>
          <li>There are no set teams, so you will play with new and interesting people everygame.</li>
        </ul>
        <h3 class="card-title">Discord Link</h3>
        <ul class="card-text">
          <% if(!user || !user.registered){ %>
            <li><i>You must sign up to see the Discord link.</i></li>
          <%}else{ %>
            <li><a href="https://discord.gg/3Q2n2Dt" target="_blank"><b>https://discord.gg/3Q2n2Dt</b></a></li>
          <%}%>
        </ul>

        <!--<h3 class="card-title">Future expansion</h3>
